milestones.description: Tony Greig has broken the record for most sixes (2) in ODIs for ENG, going past Brian Close's 1
Tony Greig has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (2) in ODIs for ENG, going past Brian Close's 1
Geoff Boycott has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6), going past Fletcher
Bevan Congdon has become the top wicket-taker for NZ in ODIs with 5 wickets, going past Dayle Hadlee's 4
Glenn Turner has broken the record for most catches (2) in ODIs for NZ, going past Peter Coman's 1
Geoff Boycott has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6) for ENG, going past Fletcher
Mark Burgess has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for NZ, going past Collinge
Collinge has conceded the most runs in an innings (52) in ODIs for NZ, going past Hadlee's record of 37
